Events Information
Classes & Programs
See a listing of the recreational programs, senior classes, workshops, and after-school programs and camps offered by Palmetto Bay.
Upcoming Events
Check out the upcoming events planned for our Village residents.
Camps and After School Programs
Here's information about our camps and recreational programs.
Environmentalist & Youth Environmentalist of the Year
Learn about the Mayor's Environmentalist and Youth Environmentalist of the Year award program and see photos of past and present award winners.
Past Events
Check our videos and photos of events that took place earlier in the year.
Sponsorship Opportunities
Become a sponsor for one of our many popular community events and get noticed!  Download our sponsorship package and rate information.
Event Videos
Check out our various community events!
Contact Us
Contact the Events division for inquiries and information concerning Village events, vendor information and sponsorship opportunities.
